---
description: 
globs: *.ts,*.svelte
alwaysApply: false
---
- Add `// SECTION` comments to group imports together, e.g. `//SVELTE`, `// DB`, `// API`, `// DRIZZLE`, `// COMPONENTS`, `// I18N`, `// TYPES`.
- The imports should be ordered
    1. Framework : Svelte imports are grouped together at the top
    2. Third Party : Group imports by the library that provides them, e.g. `//  Drizzle`, `// Zod`, `// Maplibre`
    3. Library : Our own imports are grouped by their domain, e.g. `//DB`  `//API` `//SERVICES`, `//COMPONENTS`
    4. Types : ALWAYS put all types here no matter whether they are our own or third-party. 